$(function(){$("i").click(function(){$("#main").animate({scrollTop:0},1000);});});function set2fig(b){var a;if(b<10){a="0"+b;}else{a=b;}return a;}function showClock(){var d=new Date();
var a=set2fig(d.getHours());var b=set2fig(d.getMinutes());var c=set2fig(d.getSeconds());var e=a+":"+b+":"+c;document.getElementById("clock").innerHTML=e;
}setInterval("showClock()",1);